events.name: 盗賊砦　略奪品置き場

parameters:
Is this the place where they keep the
plundered goods?\n< Serena >
エリカ HK_ST01-1
エリカ HK_ST01-1

Yeah. I've been dragged here a few
times...\n< Erika >
?\n< Serena >
No... it's nothing.\n< Erika >

Anyway, I saw it when I was brought here
before... It should be around here...\n< Erika >
...Liquor?\n< Serena >

Yeah, the boss here is a pesky one.
Despite being a mere thugs, he's been
collecting distilled spirits.\n< Erika >

Distilled spirits are expensive. Not too
pricey to touch, but not something you'd
buy casually either.\n< Erika >

So I thought I might help myself to a
little...\n< Erika >
Hm, is this wine? Oh, it's vintage.\n< Erika >

What?! Wasn't this supposed to be about
planning our escape?!\n< Serena >

Lady Erika, I said we could wreak havoc,
but this is...!\n< Serena >

No no, of course it's for our escape.
This talk about distilled spirits is
actually quite important...\n< Erika >

And conveniently, there's a torch here
too. Very good, very good.\n< Erika >
\n< Serena >??
エリカ DS_ST01-1
エリカ DS_ST01-1

*cough*...*hack*...***Cough, cough***!...heh!
heh! heh!\n< Erika >

Fire... I've heard that alcohol burns
easily, but I never expected it to blaze
up like this...\n< Serena >

It's a common trick among sailors.
Distilled spirits especially burn really
well.\n< Erika >

Those guys are in a panic because of the
fire. With this smoke, we can escape
easily.\n< Serena >
Serves them right... Hold on a sec.\n< Erika >
Oh, my gear... dumped here like trash...\n< Erika >

The contents are... Damn, no money or
medicine...\n< Erika >

Oh! But the fools! They left the
grenades! These are the most valuable of
all!\n< Erika >

Erika-dono! If we dawdle, we'll be
caught up in the fire too!\n< Serena >

I know! Damn, I guess I have to give up
on the armor... At least let me grab my
belt pouch and boots...\n< Erika >

Sorry Serena! Kept you waiting! Now I
can fight a bit!!\n< Erika >
\n< Serena >Let's go!
\n< Serena >I have no business on the third floor.
